Last Comic Standing - Season 9, Episode 1




The Premiere

Last Comic Standing is back for Season 9! One hundred of the nation's top stand-up comics have come to Hollywood to fight it out in a hilarious, winner-take-all competition - with $250,000 and an NBC development deal at stake. A brand-new host, Anthony Jeselnik, presides over all the action, and judges Roseanne Barr, Norm Macdonald and Keenen Ivory Wayans are the ultimate arbiters of comedy perfection.




Original Air Date: 22-Jul-2015
